tafsir[2]{c,v,t}:
  43,37,"Man, on the basis of his false assumptions, worships angels when angels themselves proclaim the greatness of the one and only God, at all times."
  43,46,"Throughout history, people have ignored the call of the preachers of Truth. They forget that the preachers of Truth endeavour to spread God’s word which will in any case reign supreme, however much the unbelievers may oppose them."